data.description: LARGE 4 BR NW 2.5 acre Estate Home Close To Town on SOLAR!!! Nestled on 2.5 acres of the NW is this 2,815 sq ft open floor plan ranch style estate that radiates warmth and comfort. Boasting a large master suite with attached office, 3 large bedrooms and 2.75 baths, it's perfect for a growing family or hosting guests for large get togethers. With a solar system and private, covered, well being rebuilt in 2017 this property ensures sustainability. The large outdoor barn is perfect for covered corrals to add a touch of country charm for the equestrian family and animal lovers. Enjoy an in ground jacuzzi on those cooler winter days with a view of the Sierras in the background. The large island kitchen opens to the large living room with the sizable rock fireplace. Plenty of space in the split floor plan of the larger sized bedrooms. Master br features an attached office with plenty of light through multiple access doors to jacuzzi area. The covered patio adds to the shade of the large mature trees along the privacy fence line on those warm summer days in a quiet, well established neighborhood.  Loan is assumable with VA benefit and cash/gap loan. Make this the country home you've always wanted with all the amenities close by!
